other_tests.findings: The liver demonstrates normal echotexture without suspicious focal lesions. There is no evidence of intrahepatic biliary ductal dilatation. The gallbladder is nondistended. Multiple gallstones are seen within its lumen. There is no gallbladder wall edema. No pericholecystic fluid collection. The CBD is of normal caliber measuring 2 mm. The pancreas is largely obscured by overlying bowel gas. There is no ascites.
